The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Murali-Ntini battle in offing 

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: The upcoming series between Sri Lanka and South Africa will not only witness a battle between the two, but a clash between the worlds top two bowlers as well. 

While Sri Lankan offie Muttiah Muralidharan is listed as No. 1 in the International Cricket Council (ICC)s Test bowlers rankings ? as per an ICC release on Tuesday ? South African Makhaya Ntini is hot on his heels at No. 2. 

 Australian Ricky Ponting maintained his position at 

 the top of the leaderboard in the batsmens list, followed 

 by Team India captain Rahul Dravid and Inzamam-ul Haq of 

 Pakistan. 

